[
    {
        "text": "Reverend Pinckney once said, \"Across the South, we have a deep appreciation of history.\"",
        "startTime": 3041,
        "endTime": 8250,
        "slowStartTime": 4711,
        "slowEndTime": 12600
    },
    {
        "text": "\"We haven't always had a deep appreciation of each other's history.\"",
        "startTime": 9801,
        "endTime": 12744,
        "slowStartTime": 14851,
        "slowEndTime": 19341
    },
    {
        "text": "What is true in the South is true for America.",
        "startTime": 23293,
        "endTime": 25785,
        "slowStartTime": 35090,
        "slowEndTime": 38903
    },
    {
        "text": "Clem understood that justice grows out of recognition of ourselves in each other.",
        "startTime": 28320,
        "endTime": 36672,
        "slowStartTime": 42630,
        "slowEndTime": 55233
    },
    {
        "text": "That my liberty depends on you being free, too.",
        "startTime": 38877,
        "endTime": 42482,
        "slowStartTime": 58465,
        "slowEndTime": 63948
    },
    {
        "text": "That history can't be a sword to justify injustice, or a shield against progress,...",
        "startTime": 46217,
        "endTime": 55333,
        "slowStartTime": 69475,
        "slowEndTime": 83224
    },
    {
        "text": "...but must be a manual for how to avoid repeating the mistakes of the past.",
        "startTime": 57469,
        "endTime": 61448,
        "slowStartTime": 86354,
        "slowEndTime": 92397
    },
    {
        "text": "How to break the cycle.",
        "startTime": 62906,
        "endTime": 64169,
        "slowStartTime": 94509,
        "slowEndTime": 96479
    },
    {
        "text": "A roadway toward a better world.",
        "startTime": 65252,
        "endTime": 68507,
        "slowStartTime": 98028,
        "slowEndTime": 102985
    },
    {
        "text": "He knew that the path of grace involves an open mind...",
        "startTime": 71399,
        "endTime": 77135,
        "slowStartTime": 107249,
        "slowEndTime": 115928
    },
    {
        "text": "...but, more importantly, an open heart.",
        "startTime": 79070,
        "endTime": 80693,
        "slowStartTime": 118755,
        "slowEndTime": 121264
    },
    {
        "text": "That's what I've felt this week: an open heart.",
        "startTime": 84314,
        "endTime": 87731,
        "slowStartTime": 126621,
        "slowEndTime": 131822
    },
    {
        "text": "That, more than any particular policy or analysis,...",
        "startTime": 90479,
        "endTime": 94409,
        "slowStartTime": 135869,
        "slowEndTime": 141838
    },
    {
        "text": "...is what's called upon right now, I think.",
        "startTime": 95963,
        "endTime": 97898,
        "slowStartTime": 144095,
        "slowEndTime": 147072
    }
]